<h2>Understanding marks on beer labels</h2>
<p>
  Beer labels can carry many different logos and marks. Some are EU legal protections tied to geography
  or tradition. Others are certifications granted by independent bodies, membership marks from trade
  associations, or competition awards. Knowing what each type of mark actually means — and what it
  doesn't — helps you interpret labels more accurately.
</p>

